          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Individual Rate Simplification Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to revise individual income tax rates to establish a 20% rate on taxable income of $1 million or less and a 30% rate on taxable income over $1 million for taxable years beginning after December 31, 2015. The bill requires an annual inflation adjustment to the $1 million threshold amount in taxable years beginning after 2016. </p>]]></text>
